              ],
              "studentName" : "Olivia Williams",
              "totalPoints" : 24,
              "transcript" : "Good thesis on income inequality. Clear position. Uses three sources from the syllabus which is great. Analysis is decent but could go deeper in places - tends to summarize rather than analyze. Organization is good. Intro and conclusion match well. Some paragraphs could use better topic sentences. Writing is clear. A few comma splices. Citations look good overall."
