          "gradingRecords" : [
            {
              "feedbackGenerated" : "Your textual analysis demonstrates strong close reading skills, particularly in tracing the green light motif across chapters. Your use of specific page references grounds your argument effectively. However, your interpretation of the American Dream theme, while competent, follows a well-established critical path. For future literary analysis, challenge yourself to develop more original interpretative angles. Consider what aspects of the text haven’t been thoroughly explored in existing criticism, or how you might complicate conventional readings.",
